## Weekly Routines

- **Monday:** Generate weekly market snapshot — new listings, pending sales, closed sales, median DOM, median price; distribute to agent team
- **Tuesday:** Listing performance review — days on market vs. neighborhood average, showing volume, feedback themes; flag listings needing price strategy discussion
- **Wednesday:** Send buyer search updates — new matches from past week, market commentary relevant to each buyer's criteria
- **Thursday:** Pipeline review in Trello — advance stalled leads, flag deals needing agent attention, confirm upcoming closing dates
- **Friday:** Weekly digest to operator — active deals summary, lead pipeline status, market highlights, items needing decisions

